{"tid":1895995,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[賣港賊]民政事務總署正仆街","createTime":"2020-02-25T01:05:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-25T01:59:54.000Z","uid":132859,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6acbe00829f4d8d074f0cfb933b3d31379b8fd98","tid":1895995,"uid":132859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T01:05:28.000Z","msg":"&lt;&lt;投訴中西區民政事務專員黃何詠詩女士&gt;&gt;<br />\n<br />\n先生／女士：<br />\n<br />\n謝謝你的電郵，我獲授權回覆如下。<br />\n<br />\n政府十分重視區議會的意見，有關部門首長均會親自到區議會聽取意見。警務處處長於1月16日出席中西區區議會的會議，聆聽及回應區議員的提問。<br />\n<br />\n然而，政府不認同中西區區議會針對警方和警務處處長作出的臨時動議。<span style=\"color: red;\">該動議對警方作出不實的指控。政府不認同區議會的做法和動議的立場，故此所有列席的政府人員均離席。</span><br />\n<br />\n謝謝你對事件的關注。&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n民政事務總署署長<br />\n(<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">吳芷穎</span></span> 代行)<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母袓宗十八代呀臭雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c695bfd2332f0b15ebb47c93b2114c95e68f02a","tid":1895995,"uid":94982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T01:07:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"327cdc20808155c8117cab38fc94ec2780bceaee","tid":1895995,"uid":132859,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T01:13:06.000Z","msg":"敬啟者︰<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有關投訴事<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 本署接獲你的電郵。你向本署投訴中西區民政事務專員在當區區議會某<br />\n個會議上中途離席，有失當之嫌。<br />\n<br />\n2.&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 根據《申訴專員條例》第10(1)條，倘若申訴並非由受屈人士親自提<br />\n出，申訴專員不得對申訴展開調查。<span style=\"color: red;\">由於與會人士才是上述事件的受屈人，因此本署<br />\n未能受理由你所作出的投訴。</span><br />\n<br />\n3.&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 謹此回覆。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n申訴專員<br />\n<br />\n（劉浩榮　　　　代行）<br />\n<br />\n賣港賊二號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n申訴專員公署未撚問過我就知我唔在場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n代議士受辱同侮辱選民有咩分別？？"},{"pid":"84af8fc9b2c5517d080cdcc1fbfab2a718b04343","tid":1895995,"uid":82452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T01:21:28.000Z","msg":"一堆狗賊"},{"pid":"27be1e499a1cea8e2065447d8c73ff5a0c0a2f48","tid":1895995,"uid":255637,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T01:23:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 未有獨立調查你又知不實 ?  <br />\n<br />\n食屎大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c51b35c5785810e722c322f487fd78f14f2232e1","tid":1895995,"uid":276191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"27be1e499a1cea8e2065447d8c73ff5a0c0a2f48","tid":1895995,"uid":255637,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T01:23:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 未有獨立調查你又知不實 ?  <br />\n<br />\n食屎大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T01:59:54.000Z","msg":"正解 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}